nodes.text: Naomi Ackie (born November 2, 1992) is a British actress who played Jannah in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. She is best known for her role on Star Wars and for starring as Bonnie in the second season of comedy series The End of the F***ing World. She is also known for appearing in the 2016 film Lady Macbeth.
